item.description:
Hi all,

Our February meet-up will be Feb. 12, 2011 at 2:00pm

Alexandra Morgan's Animal School
84 Cutler St.
Warren, RI 02885
401-434-3687

Admission is $5

***JOIN US FOR OUR PUG BIRTHDAY PARTY TO CELEBRATE NOAH, ABBY AND TEDDIE'S BIRTHDAYS!!***

**For those of you attending the meet-ups, please don't forget to bring your pug's medical paperwork including a stool sample result testing negative for Giardia.**

Snacks, refreshments & "Pug Fudge" will be served as always! And if you need any info. on Pug training, boarding or daycare, Alexandra will be happy to answer any questions you may have
